HEADWORD: Acclimation
<hw>Ac`cli*ma"tion</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The process
of becoming, or the state of being, acclimated, or habituated to a new
climate; acclimatization.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

